          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Scales all map distances up or down together. 1.0 = defaults (a metropolis map ≈ 35 of your units across, a hamlet ≈ 1.5). Use 2 for a larger world, 0.5 for a smaller one. A single map block can override the distance entirely with a `scale:` line.",
